data.description: Start the new year off in your own home or adding to your rental portfolio.  This 3 bedroom ranch has great potential. Located just 24 miles from St. Louis Lambert airport - this home is centrally located to major roadways along with plenty of shopping, businesses and two hospitals close by.  Living Room, hallway and bedrooms on main level all have hardwood flooring.  The kitchen has plenty of cabinet space and provides a nice eat in size for your family.  Off the kitchen to the backyard you can sit back an relax on the nice size deck that will allow for plenty of entertainment. The steps to basement are extra wide and lead you down to the family room - where you will find a half bath and small kitchenette/bar area.  There are two bonus rooms that are partially finished for extra bonus rooms.  Home is sold as is, seller will not make any repairs nor satisfy occupancy.  Information pulled from various resources, Buyers Agent/Buyer to verify information before placing offer.
